N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 380.1 - License period

State Regulations

Application for a license to act as a dealer pursuant to
article 20 of the Agricultural and Markets Law shall be submitted to the
commissioner on or before April 1st in each year for the license year beginning

May 1st following. Notes
